lead_paragraph: Miami Dolphins owner Stephen Ross says his latest shake-up of the organization paid off in the draft, including unanimity about the risky decision to take Ole Miss tackle Laremy Tunsil.

headline.print_headline: Dolphins Owner Says Team's Latest Shake-Up Pays Off in Draft
